# Copy to .env.local and fill in. All keys are NEXT_PUBLIC_ because this app runs as
# a static export — server-side secrets are not available.
#
# These two enable:
#   - device-id based anon auth (no signup) backed by Supabase
#   - Postgres-backed lesson progress, race scores, leaderboard
#   - Realtime presence (G006), co-op rooms (G007), race matches (G008)
#
# Without them the app still runs fully (G001-G004) using localStorage and a
# simulated presence counter; multiplayer pages will show a "not configured" notice.

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
